  - given-names: Mattia
    family-names: Calastri
repository-code: 'https://github.com/FedericoCasarella/super-agent'
abstract: >-
  A self-hosted personal AI agent that lives in Telegram,
  reasons with the Claude Code CLI, and keeps an
  Obsidian-style markdown second brain it can act on through
  pluggable connectors exposed over the Model Context
  Protocol. Designed around a human-in-the-loop principle:
  irreversible actions are proposed for approval, never
  auto-executed.
keywords:
